<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Immigration officials have a sense of humour, right?</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/8578097/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Immigration officials have a sense of humour, right?" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/8/8578097_29a6dc0292_m.jpg" height="240" width="180" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>The location?  Outside the JFK Building, home of the Boston branch of the US Immigration Services.</p>

<p>The occassion?  Just successfully had my Green Card interview.</p>

<p>The T-shirt?  A gift from my sister.  It reads "I ordered by bride from paulfrank.com"</p>

<p>The shirt?  Stayed buttoned-up the whole time I was inside.</p>
        </p>

